'''誓言守护者'''（{{lang-en|Oath Keepers}}，或译'''守誓者'''）是一个美国[[极右翼|极右翼]]<ref name="apctferg2015">{{Cite news|author=<!--AP Wire but Tribune site gives reporter contact info-->|title=Return of armed militia group Oath Keepers to Ferguson raises concern|work=[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]|agency=Associated Press|date=2015-08-11|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/nationworld/ct-ferguson-oath-keepers-armed-militia-20150811-story.html|accessdate=2015-08-14|quote=[Ferguson 2015] wearing camouflage bulletproof vests and openly carrying rifles and pistols on West Florissant Avenue|archivedate=2015-08-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813134235/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/nationworld/ct-ferguson-oath-keepers-armed-militia-20150811-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>民兵组织<ref name="wpferg2014">{{Cite news|author=McCoy|first=Terrence|title=The Oath Keepers: The Little-known Militia Now Roaming the Streets of Ferguson|work=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|date=2014-01-01|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2014/12/01/the-oath-keepers-the-militant-militia-now-roaming-the-streets-of-ferguson|accessdate=2016-12-01|archivedate=2017-10-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028200935/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2014/12/01/the-oath-keepers-the-militant-militia-now-roaming-the-streets-of-ferguson/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該組織由现役和已退役的美國军人、警察和[[第一响应者|第一响应者]]组成<ref name="OathKeepersAboutUs2">{{cite web|title=About Oath Keepers|url=https://www.oathkeepers.org/about/|date=November 6, 2014|publisher=Oath Keepers|website=oathkeepers.com|access-date=20 March 2016|archive-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403071616/https://www.oathkeepers.org/about/|url-status=no}}</ref>。[[联邦调查局|美國联邦调查局]]認定 "誓言守护者 "为一个 "准军事组织"，是一个规模庞大但组织松散的民兵集合体，[[联邦调查局|美國联邦调查局]]還認定誓言守护者主張美國联邦政府被一个试图剥夺美国公民权利的阴谋所控制<ref name="CincyEnq">{{Cite news|author=Sparling|first=Hannah K.|author2=Kevin Grasha|title=Ohio militias: Who are the Oath Keepers, Ohio State Regular Militia?|url=https://www.cincinnati.com/story/news/2021/01/21/ohio-militias-who-oath-keepers-ohio-state-regular-militia/4231869001/|accessdate=31 January 2021|agency=Cincinnati Enquirer|date=January 22, 2021}}</ref>。[[南方贫困法律中心|南方贫困法律中心]]認定该组织信奉[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]以及一些与[[白人至上主义|白人至上主义]]有關的法律理论<ref name="Lenz2013">{{Cite web|title=Oath Keepers Rally Reveals Radical Politics of Group|url=https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2013/07/25/oath-keepers-rally-reveals-radical-politics-group|accessdate=20 March 2016|author=Lenz|date=July 25, 2013|first=Ryan|publisher=[[南方贫困法律中心|南方贫困法律中心]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309204552/https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2013/07/25/oath-keepers-rally-reveals-radical-politics-group|archivedate=2016-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Keller2009Jul">{{Cite web|title=Evidence Grows of Far-Right Militia Resurgence|url=https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/intelligence-report/2009/evidence-grows-far-right-militia-resurgence|accessdate=20 March 2016|author=Keller|first=Larry|publisher=[[南方贫困法律中心|南方贫困法律中心]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310122508/https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/intelligence-report/2009/evidence-grows-far-right-militia-resurgence|archivedate=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Lenz2011">{{Cite web|title=Are the Oath Keepers Fighting 'Martial Law'?|url=https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/intelligence-report/2011/are-oath-keepers-fighting-%E2%80%98martial-law%E2%80%99|accessdate=20 March 2016|author=Lenz|first=Ryan|work=splcenter.org|publisher=[[南方贫困法律中心|南方贫困法律中心]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310113731/https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/intelligence-report/2011/are-oath-keepers-fighting-%E2%80%98martial-law%E2%80%99|archivedate=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

